<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Quarterly Practice Compliance Summary — {{ practice_name }} — Q{{ period_quarter }} {{ period_year }}</title>
<style>
@page {
    size: Letter;
    margin: 0.75in;
    @bottom-center {
        content: "Issued by {{ presenter_brand }}.  Verify: {{ verify_phone }} or {{ verify_url_short }}.  Valid until {{ valid_until_human }}.";
        font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
        font-size: 9pt;
        color: #666;
    }
}
body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    color: #222;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-size: 11pt;
}
.letterhead {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #14A89E;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.letterhead h1 {
    font-size: 24pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a365d;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}
.letterhead .practice-name {
    font-size: 16pt;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
}
.letterhead .period {
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0;
}
.statement {
    margin: 18px 0;
    font-size: 11pt;
    line-height: 1.55;
}
.statement p {
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
}
.summary-grid {
    width: 7.0in;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 14px 0 18px 0;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
}
.summary-grid th, .summary-grid td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 7px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}
.summary-grid th {
    color: #4a5568;
    font-weight: 600;
    width: 60%;
}
.summary-grid td {
    color: #1a365d;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
}
.signoff {
    margin-top: 22px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}
.signoff .role-line {
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
}
.signoff .signed-by {
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0;
}
.signoff .signature-row {
    margin-top: 22px;
    display: block;
}
.signoff .signature-line {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 60%;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2d3748;
    height: 22px;
}
.signoff .signature-label {
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #718096;
    margin-top: 4px;
    display: block;
}
.attestation-block {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #f7fafc;
    border-left: 3px solid #14A89E;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #4a5568;
}
.attestation-block .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.attestation-block .hash {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    word-break: break-all;
}
.disclaimer {
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: #718096;
    line-height: 1.4;
}
.disclaimer p { margin: 0 0 6px 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="letterhead">
    <h1>Quarterly Practice Compliance Summary</h1>
    <p class="practice-name">{{ practice_name }}</p>
    <p class="period">Q{{ period_quarter }} {{ period_year }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; {{ period_start_human }} through {{ period_end_human }}</p>
</div>

<div class="statement">
    <p>
        This summary documents that <strong>{{ practice_name }}</strong> operated a HIPAA Security Rule technical-safeguard monitoring program for the calendar quarter above. From {{ period_start_human }} through {{ period_end_human }}, the practice's technical safeguards were monitored on a continuous automated schedule across {{ sites_count }} site{{ 's' if sites_count != 1 else '' }}, {{ appliances_count }} compliance appliance{{ 's' if appliances_count != 1 else '' }}, and {{ workstations_count }} workstation{{ 's' if workstations_count != 1 else '' }}. Cryptographically signed evidence bundles ({{ bundle_count }} for the period) were captured and chained, supporting the practice's §164.308(a)(1)(ii)(D) information-system-activity-review obligation. The full check catalog is available on request.
    </p>
    <p>
        This document is intended for the practice's §164.530(j) records-retention archive. The Privacy Officer reviews the quarterly summary and signs below to attest that the period's evidence has been reviewed.
    </p>
</div>

<table class="summary-grid">
    <tr>
        <th>Signed evidence bundles captured</th>
        <td>{{ bundle_count }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>OpenTimestamps anchor coverage</th>
        <td>{{ ots_anchored_pct_str }}%</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Compliance issues detected (period)</th>
        <td>{{ drift_detected_count }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Compliance issues resolved (period)</th>
        <td>{{ drift_resolved_count }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Mean compliance score (period)</th>
        <td>{{ mean_score_str }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Monitored check types</th>
        <td>{{ monitored_check_types_count }}</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="signoff">
    <p class="role-line">Reviewed and attested by <strong>{{ privacy_officer_name }}</strong>, {{ privacy_officer_title }} — Privacy Officer designation.</p>
    <p class="signed-by">Email: {{ privacy_officer_email }}</p>
    <span class="signature-row">
        <span class="signature-line"></span>
        <span class="signature-label">Privacy Officer signature &nbsp;·&nbsp; Date</span>
    </span>
</div>

<div class="attestation-block">
    <p><span class="label">Issued by:</span> {{ presenter_brand }}{{ presenter_contact_line }}</p>
    <p><span class="label">Issuance:</span> {{ issued_at_human }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; <span class="label">Valid until:</span> {{ valid_until_human }} (365 days)</p>
    <p><span class="label">Attestation hash:</span> <span class="hash">{{ attestation_hash }}</span></p>
    <p><span class="label">Verify:</span> {{ verify_phone }} or {{ verify_url_short }}/{{ attestation_hash[:32] }}</p>
</div>

<div class="disclaimer">
    <p>This summary is audit-supportive technical evidence; it is not a HIPAA §164.528 disclosure accounting and does not constitute a legal opinion. It contains no patient-identifying information and is not part of any designated record set under §164.524. Detailed technical evidence (cryptographically signed bundles + chain + OpenTimestamps anchors) is available on request to the practice's carrier, legal counsel, or auditor. To report a concern, contact compliance@osiriscare.com (best-effort acknowledgment within 7 business days; substantive response within 30 days) or the HHS Office for Civil Rights at hhs.gov/ocr/complaints.</p>
    <p>The practice retains independent copies of this summary for §164.530(j) records-retention compliance. Attestation-hash verification is supported through the term of the {{ presenter_brand }} relationship plus a commercially reasonable wind-down period.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
